item.title: Air quality
item.description: Air quality The air quality data provides information on levels of various air pollutants, including particles, nitrogen dioxide and ground-level ozone, in Swedish cities and in rural areas. The data is provided in cooperation with SMHI. See Luftkvaliteten i realtid och preliminär statistik for more information (Swedish). License & conditions The data is licensed under Creative Commons Zero, CC0.
